Hello,
 
Thank you for your email.
Could you please tell me your availability for this week so that we can arrange a remote session via Zoom to remove the erroneous patch? 
For the remote session you will need to have Putty installed on your computer as I would need to access the server via SSH.
 
Have a nice day,
Best regards,
Alin Anca
